1
00:02:34,230 --> 00:02:36,090
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Good morning, Bastian.</font>

2
00:02:56,210 --> 00:03:00,050
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I had another dream, Dad, about Mom.</font>

3
00:03:04,450 --> 00:03:06,120
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I understand, son.</font>

4
00:03:08,020 --> 00:03:10,520
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But we have to get on with things, right?</font>

5
00:03:23,470 --> 00:03:26,100
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Bastian, we each have responsibilities.</font>

6
00:03:28,140 --> 00:03:29,900
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">We can't let Mom's death...</font>

7
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:33,940
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...be an excuse
for not getting the job done, right?</font>

8
00:03:35,110 --> 00:03:36,080
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Yes.</font>

9
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:54,620
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Son, it's time you and I had a talk.</font>

10
00:03:58,830 --> 00:04:01,860
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I got a call from your math teacher
yesterday.</font>

11
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:07,540
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">She says that you were...</font>

12
00:04:07,870 --> 00:04:10,100
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...drawing horses in your math book.</font>

13
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:12,870
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Unicorns. They were unicorns.</font>

14
00:04:13,540 --> 00:04:14,440
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What?</font>

15
00:04:16,840 --> 00:04:17,680
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Nothing.</font>

16
00:04:17,840 --> 00:04:21,180
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">She also says you don't
do your homework on time.</font>

17
00:04:25,380 --> 00:04:28,620
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I'm very disappointed you didn't even
try out for the swimming team.</font>

18
00:04:31,090 --> 00:04:33,690
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">As to those riding lessons you wanted....</font>

19
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:38,890
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You say you love horses
but you're afraid to get on a real one.</font>

20
00:04:40,960 --> 00:04:44,970
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You're old enough to get your head down
out of the clouds and...</font>

21
00:04:45,900 --> 00:04:48,230
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...and keep both feet on the ground.</font>

22
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:52,570
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Okay.</font>

23
00:05:00,110 --> 00:05:04,780
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Stop daydreaming.
Start facing your problems. Okay?</font>

24
00:05:09,550 --> 00:05:13,620
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">There, I think we've had a nice talk.</font>

25
00:05:14,420 --> 00:05:16,490
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">We should have more.</font>

26
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:19,560
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Have a good day, son.
Don't be late for school again.</font>

27
00:05:19,890 --> 00:05:22,390
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But, yesterday I wasn't.</font>

28
00:05:27,900 --> 00:05:30,230
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Hey, it's the weirdo.</font>

29
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:34,400
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Weirdo, you got any cash for us today?</font>

30
00:05:39,740 --> 00:05:41,540
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Let's get him !</font>

31
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:52,580
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You can't get away.</font>

32
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,750
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You're dead, chicken!</font>

33
00:05:54,850 --> 00:05:56,090
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">We'll get you!</font>

34
00:05:59,420 --> 00:06:01,590
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">-Where's your money?
-I don't have any!</font>

35
00:06:01,660 --> 00:06:04,060
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">No money? Mamma's boy is holding out.</font>

36
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:07,930
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">If you ain't got money,
you go in the garbage.</font>

37
00:06:16,670 --> 00:06:19,540
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Maybe the chicken can lay an egg in there.</font>

38
00:06:26,510 --> 00:06:29,280
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Who said you could get out of the garbage?</font>

39
00:06:29,380 --> 00:06:31,120
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Get back in there.</font>

40
00:06:31,220 --> 00:06:32,580
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Not again.</font>

41
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:34,590
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Not again!</font>

42
00:06:34,690 --> 00:06:36,520
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Where are you going, wimp?</font>

43
00:06:45,460 --> 00:06:47,900
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">-He went that way.
-Which way?</font>

44
00:06:53,030 --> 00:06:56,000
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Get out of here! I don't like kids.</font>

45
00:07:11,550 --> 00:07:14,450
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Are you still here? Didn't you hear me?</font>

46
00:07:15,020 --> 00:07:16,490
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You're hiding, aren't you?</font>

47
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:19,590
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The video arcade is down the street.</font>

48
00:07:20,390 --> 00:07:24,730
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Here we just sell small rectangular objects.
They're called books.</font>

49
00:07:25,390 --> 00:07:28,330
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">They require effort and make no beeps.</font>

50
00:07:28,390 --> 00:07:29,400
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">On your way.</font>

51
00:07:29,460 --> 00:07:33,330
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I know books. I have 186 of them at home.</font>

52
00:07:33,870 --> 00:07:34,900
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Comic books.</font>

53
00:07:34,970 --> 00:07:36,800
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">No, I've read Treasure lsland...</font>

54
00:07:36,970 --> 00:07:39,270
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">... The Last of the Mohicans, Wizard of Oz...</font>

55
00:07:39,340 --> 00:07:42,310
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...Lord of the Rings,
20,000 Leagues Under the Sea, Tarzan.</font>

56
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:49,050
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Who are you running away from?</font>

57
00:07:53,750 --> 00:07:55,420
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Some kids from school.</font>

58
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:57,180
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Why?</font>

59
00:07:58,520 --> 00:08:00,390
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">They threw me in the garbage.</font>

60
00:08:00,620 --> 00:08:02,620
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Why not punch them in the nose?</font>

61
00:08:05,930 --> 00:08:07,430
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I don't know.</font>

62
00:08:13,430 --> 00:08:15,430
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What's that book about?</font>

63
00:08:16,970 --> 00:08:20,140
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Oh, this is something special.</font>

64
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:28,440
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Well, what is it?</font>

65
00:08:31,280 --> 00:08:32,180
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Look.</font>

66
00:08:33,450 --> 00:08:36,120
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Your books are safe.</font>

67
00:08:37,450 --> 00:08:39,280
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">While you're reading them...</font>

68
00:08:39,450 --> 00:08:44,390
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...you get to become
Tarzan or Robinson Crusoe.</font>

69
00:08:44,460 --> 00:08:46,620
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But that's what I like about them.</font>

70
00:08:46,790 --> 00:08:50,630
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But afterwards you get to be
a little boy again.</font>

71
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,960
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What do you mean?</font>

72
00:08:53,460 --> 00:08:54,630
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Listen.</font>

73
00:08:57,330 --> 00:08:58,830
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Have you ever been...</font>

74
00:08:59,970 --> 00:09:01,300
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...Captain Nemo...</font>

75
00:09:02,170 --> 00:09:07,110
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...trapped inside your submarine
while the giant squid is attacking you?</font>

76
00:09:09,780 --> 00:09:10,580
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Yes.</font>

77
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:13,310
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Weren't you afraid you couldn't escape?</font>

78
00:09:14,010 --> 00:09:15,580
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But it's only a story.</font>

79
00:09:15,850 --> 00:09:18,320
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">That's what I'm talking about.</font>

80
00:09:19,020 --> 00:09:20,850
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The ones you read...</font>

81
00:09:21,190 --> 00:09:22,320
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...are safe.</font>

82
00:09:25,690 --> 00:09:27,160
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">And that one isn't?</font>

83
00:09:29,690 --> 00:09:31,190
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Don't worry about it.</font>

84
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:33,830
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But you just said it was--</font>

85
00:09:41,800 --> 00:09:43,470
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Forget about it.</font>

86
00:09:44,170 --> 00:09:47,370
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">This book is not for you.</font>

87
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:58,580
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Koreander's.</font>

88
00:10:00,680 --> 00:10:02,690
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What can I do for you?</font>

89
00:10:10,590 --> 00:10:12,930
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">They run maybe 300, 370....</font>

90
00:10:13,590 --> 00:10:15,460
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">It will take me a couple of a weeks.</font>

91
00:11:08,770 --> 00:11:11,610
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Math test. Oh, no!</font>

92
00:12:15,460 --> 00:12:18,590
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"lt was midnight in the Howling Forest.</font>

93
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:23,130
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"The wind whistled
through the tops of the ancient trees.</font>

94
00:12:23,470 --> 00:12:25,800
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"Suddenly, something enormous...</font>

95
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:29,840
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"...crashed and rumbled
through the eerie woods. "</font>

96
00:12:55,720 --> 00:12:56,890
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What's that?</font>

97
00:13:33,020 --> 00:13:34,620
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Excuse me...</font>

98
00:13:35,050 --> 00:13:39,060
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...but would it be all right
if I joined you this evening?</font>

99
00:13:41,360 --> 00:13:45,700
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You see, I've been traveling all day.</font>

100
00:14:11,050 --> 00:14:14,990
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Now I see why you picked this camp.</font>

101
00:14:26,560 --> 00:14:30,070
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">A delicious looking limestone rock!</font>

102
00:14:33,770 --> 00:14:35,640
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Nice bouquet.</font>

103
00:14:36,270 --> 00:14:39,970
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Must be a real vintage year.</font>

104
00:14:42,040 --> 00:14:44,010
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Yes, you're right.</font>

105
00:14:44,480 --> 00:14:47,510
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Those delicious rocks
are the reason we've camped here.</font>

106
00:14:49,380 --> 00:14:52,950
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">-Is he a nutcase?
-No, he's a Rock Biter.</font>

107
00:14:53,190 --> 00:14:54,380
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">A Rock Biter!</font>

108
00:15:10,230 --> 00:15:12,570
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">-Sorry.
-Poor baby.</font>

109
00:15:17,040 --> 00:15:18,540
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Pardon me.</font>

110
00:15:20,010 --> 00:15:24,210
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">That was limestone, with a dash of quartz.</font>

111
00:15:25,980 --> 00:15:27,680
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Very tasty.</font>

112
00:15:28,810 --> 00:15:33,720
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Where I come from in the North,
we us to have exquisite gourmet rocks.</font>

113
00:15:36,320 --> 00:15:37,720
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Only now...</font>

114
00:15:38,690 --> 00:15:40,020
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...now...</font>

115
00:15:41,160 --> 00:15:43,260
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...they're all gone.</font>

116
00:15:44,020 --> 00:15:46,190
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I know how it happened.</font>

117
00:15:46,860 --> 00:15:49,360
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I swear it wasn't me.</font>

118
00:15:51,500 --> 00:15:53,930
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I think I know what it was. Tell us more.</font>

119
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:58,300
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Near my home,
there used to be a beautiful lake...</font>

120
00:15:59,140 --> 00:16:00,470
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...but then...</font>

121
00:16:01,040 --> 00:16:03,870
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...then it was gone.</font>

122
00:16:04,310 --> 00:16:06,180
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Did the lake dry up?</font>

123
00:16:06,810 --> 00:16:09,580
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">No. It just wasn't there anymore.</font>

124
00:16:09,850 --> 00:16:14,520
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Nothing was there anymore.
Not even a dried-up lake.</font>

125
00:16:15,380 --> 00:16:16,280
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">A hole?</font>

126
00:16:16,350 --> 00:16:20,520
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">A hole would be something.
No, it was Nothing.</font>

127
00:16:21,420 --> 00:16:24,890
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">And it got bigger and bigger.</font>

128
00:16:26,020 --> 00:16:28,730
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">First, there was no lake anymore.</font>

129
00:16:28,790 --> 00:16:32,530
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">And then, finally, no rocks.</font>

130
00:16:38,700 --> 00:16:43,310
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">If he keeps stuffing his face like that,
soon there won't be any rocks here either.</font>

131
00:16:44,340 --> 00:16:46,810
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Night Hob, this could be serious!</font>

132
00:16:47,510 --> 00:16:48,740
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Rock Biter...</font>

133
00:16:48,810 --> 00:16:51,980
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...what you told us is also happening
where I live in the West.</font>

134
00:16:52,050 --> 00:16:55,150
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">A strange sort of Nothing
is destroying everything.</font>

135
00:16:55,220 --> 00:16:59,650
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Yes. We Night Hobs live in the South
and it's there, too.</font>

136
00:17:00,020 --> 00:17:05,860
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">So, it's not just in our part of Fantasia?</font>

137
00:17:06,890 --> 00:17:10,860
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Maybe, it's already everywhere.</font>

138
00:17:17,800 --> 00:17:20,570
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Maybe our whole land is in danger.</font>

139
00:17:21,640 --> 00:17:22,940
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What can we do?</font>

140
00:17:23,270 --> 00:17:27,980
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">My people are sending me to
the Ivory Tower, to the Empress, for help.</font>

141
00:17:28,180 --> 00:17:29,810
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">We are on the same--</font>

142
00:17:30,610 --> 00:17:35,250
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">We are on the same mission.
After all, if the Empress can't save us...</font>

143
00:17:35,610 --> 00:17:36,810
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...who could?</font>

144
00:17:36,950 --> 00:17:39,420
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Then why are we all just sitting here...</font>

145
00:17:39,920 --> 00:17:42,720
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...instead of taking off for the Ivory Tower?</font>

146
00:17:43,350 --> 00:17:44,990
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What are we waiting for?</font>

147
00:17:45,090 --> 00:17:47,390
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Yes. Let's go now.</font>

148
00:17:47,490 --> 00:17:48,930
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Wake up!</font>

149
00:17:49,160 --> 00:17:50,560
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Come on, old girl.</font>

150
00:17:50,630 --> 00:17:52,590
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">We can't just hang around here.</font>

151
00:17:53,600 --> 00:17:55,530
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Wake up! Ready for take off.</font>

152
00:17:55,800 --> 00:17:57,730
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Oh, stupid bat!</font>

153
00:17:58,300 --> 00:18:02,240
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">We can't wait for a snail. Can I carry you?</font>

154
00:18:02,340 --> 00:18:05,710
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Don't worry. It's a racing snail.</font>

155
00:18:06,470 --> 00:18:10,610
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But we can't even wait for a racing snail.</font>

156
00:18:13,910 --> 00:18:16,250
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">It really is a racing snail.</font>

157
00:18:16,550 --> 00:18:19,720
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Nobody gives a hoot
about me and my stupid bat.</font>

158
00:18:30,060 --> 00:18:35,830
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Maybe I'll take a few of these
yummy gourmet rocks, for the road....</font>

159
00:19:00,720 --> 00:19:01,950
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The Nothing!</font>

160
00:19:18,460 --> 00:19:19,460
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Look!</font>

161
00:19:20,900 --> 00:19:22,570
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">There it is!</font>

162
00:19:23,330 --> 00:19:26,000
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The heart of Fantasia !</font>

163
00:19:46,690 --> 00:19:50,660
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I never knew it was that beautiful.</font>

164
00:20:04,800 --> 00:20:05,900
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Stay awake!</font>

165
00:20:08,200 --> 00:20:10,170
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I told you to stay awake.</font>

166
00:20:57,610 --> 00:20:59,950
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The home of the Empress.</font>

167
00:21:01,010 --> 00:21:02,610
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">She's our only hope.</font>

168
00:21:36,410 --> 00:21:39,640
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Friends, I know why you are all here.</font>

169
00:21:41,040 --> 00:21:42,380
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The Nothing...</font>

170
00:21:45,110 --> 00:21:47,280
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...is destroying our world.</font>

171
00:21:49,720 --> 00:21:52,050
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I also know that you...</font>

172
00:21:52,550 --> 00:21:54,890
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...have come to beseech...</font>

173
00:21:56,060 --> 00:21:57,890
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...the Empress for help.</font>

174
00:22:02,260 --> 00:22:04,260
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But I have terrible news.</font>

175
00:22:07,560 --> 00:22:09,770
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The Empress herself
has become deathly ill.</font>

176
00:22:13,040 --> 00:22:17,910
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">There seems to be a mysterious link
between her illness and the Nothing.</font>

177
00:22:20,510 --> 00:22:22,180
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">She's dying.</font>

178
00:22:26,850 --> 00:22:30,580
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">So, she cannot save us.</font>

179
00:22:33,750 --> 00:22:35,920
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But there just might be one chance.</font>

180
00:22:40,430 --> 00:22:43,590
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The Plains People
who hunt the purple buffalo...</font>

181
00:22:43,930 --> 00:22:46,100
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...have among them a great warrior.</font>

182
00:22:46,430 --> 00:22:50,600
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">He alone has a chance
to fight the Nothing and save us.</font>

183
00:22:52,300 --> 00:22:54,300
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">He is our only hope.</font>

184
00:22:56,970 --> 00:23:00,010
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">His name is Atreyu.</font>

185
00:23:19,490 --> 00:23:21,120
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Atreyu.</font>

186
00:23:31,200 --> 00:23:34,600
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"The Empress had already
sent for the great warrior.</font>

187
00:23:35,500 --> 00:23:39,270
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"When he finally appeared
on the terrace of the Ivory Tower...</font>

188
00:23:40,010 --> 00:23:43,980
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"...he carried with him
the hopes of all Fantasia. "</font>

189
00:24:01,090 --> 00:24:03,260
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">A little boy!</font>

190
00:24:04,230 --> 00:24:08,060
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I'm sorry, but this is not
the time nor place for children.</font>

191
00:24:09,430 --> 00:24:10,700
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You must leave.</font>

192
00:24:11,030 --> 00:24:14,030
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">If you don't want me here,
you shouldn't have sent for me.</font>

193
00:24:17,470 --> 00:24:18,370
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Is he a nutcase?</font>

194
00:24:18,440 --> 00:24:21,140
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">It was not you we sent for.
We wanted Atreyu.</font>

195
00:24:21,810 --> 00:24:23,310
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I am Atreyu.</font>

196
00:24:25,380 --> 00:24:27,380
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Not Atreyu the Child.</font>

197
00:24:27,710 --> 00:24:29,340
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Atreyu the Warrior.</font>

198
00:24:29,410 --> 00:24:32,080
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I am the only Atreyu of the Plains People.</font>

199
00:24:32,420 --> 00:24:35,350
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But I'll be happy to go back
to hunting the purple buffalo.</font>

200
00:24:37,320 --> 00:24:38,220
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Wait!</font>

201
00:24:42,390 --> 00:24:44,060
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Come back, please.</font>

202
00:24:55,230 --> 00:24:58,400
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">If you really are the Atreyu we sent for...</font>

203
00:24:58,740 --> 00:25:01,400
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...you would be willing to go on a quest?</font>

204
00:25:03,570 --> 00:25:05,410
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Yes, of course.</font>

205
00:25:06,540 --> 00:25:08,210
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What kind of a quest?</font>

206
00:25:08,480 --> 00:25:10,980
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">To find a cure for the Empress...</font>

207
00:25:13,250 --> 00:25:15,250
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...and to save our world.</font>

208
00:25:16,580 --> 00:25:19,820
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">No one can give you any advice
except this:</font>

209
00:25:21,820 --> 00:25:23,490
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You must go alone.</font>

210
00:25:24,720 --> 00:25:27,230
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You must leave all your weapons behind.</font>

211
00:25:29,990 --> 00:25:31,930
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">It will be very dangerous.</font>

212
00:25:33,760 --> 00:25:35,400
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Any chance of success?</font>

213
00:25:37,500 --> 00:25:38,770
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I do not know.</font>

214
00:25:39,400 --> 00:25:41,070
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But if you fail...</font>

215
00:25:41,600 --> 00:25:44,100
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...the Empress will surely die...</font>

216
00:25:44,570 --> 00:25:47,410
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...and our whole world will be destroyed.</font>

217
00:26:08,490 --> 00:26:09,560
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">When do I begin?</font>

218
00:26:11,990 --> 00:26:14,830
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Now. And you must hurry, Atreyu.</font>

219
00:26:15,030 --> 00:26:17,360
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The Nothing grows stronger every day.</font>

220
00:26:23,970 --> 00:26:25,170
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Take this.</font>

221
00:26:34,380 --> 00:26:35,710
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The Auryn!</font>

222
00:26:41,990 --> 00:26:46,320
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">He who wears the Auryn
speaks for the Empress.</font>

223
00:26:46,920 --> 00:26:49,930
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">It will guide and protect you.</font>

224
00:27:02,970 --> 00:27:04,100
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Wake up.</font>

225
00:27:04,270 --> 00:27:05,870
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Farewell, Atreyu.</font>

226
00:27:07,210 --> 00:27:08,870
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Take care.</font>

227
00:27:46,500 --> 00:27:48,070
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"A t the same time...</font>

228
00:27:48,140 --> 00:27:52,170
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"...elsewhere in Fantasia,
a Creature of Darkness...</font>

229
00:27:52,640 --> 00:27:55,140
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"...also began his quest. "</font>

230
00:28:16,960 --> 00:28:20,960
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"They had been traveling aimlessly
for almost a week...</font>

231
00:28:21,400 --> 00:28:24,470
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"...but they couldnot find a cure
for the Empress.</font>

232
00:28:24,700 --> 00:28:29,370
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"Neither Atreyu nor his horse, Artax,
had the vaguest suspicion...</font>

233
00:28:29,840 --> 00:28:33,140
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"...that the Creature of Darkness,
the Gmork...</font>

234
00:28:33,570 --> 00:28:36,210
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"...was already tracking them down. "</font>

235
00:28:45,680 --> 00:28:47,150
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What is it, Artax?</font>

236
00:28:48,350 --> 00:28:51,520
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Is it time to go already?</font>

237
00:28:54,020 --> 00:28:57,360
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I know what you want. It's time to eat.</font>

238
00:29:01,760 --> 00:29:02,830
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Good idea.</font>

239
00:29:03,170 --> 00:29:05,400
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">No, it's a great idea !</font>

240
00:29:25,250 --> 00:29:27,680
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">No, not too much.</font>

241
00:29:28,550 --> 00:29:31,550
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">We still have a long way to go.</font>

242
00:30:35,100 --> 00:30:39,110
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"A treyu and Artax had searched
the Silver Mountains...</font>

243
00:30:39,270 --> 00:30:42,610
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"...the Desert of Shattered Hopes
and the Crystal Towers...</font>

244
00:30:43,210 --> 00:30:44,850
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"...without success.</font>

245
00:30:45,410 --> 00:30:48,420
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"And so, there was only one chance left.</font>

246
00:30:49,150 --> 00:30:51,890
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"To find Morla, the Ancient One...</font>

247
00:30:52,450 --> 00:30:54,790
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"...the wisest being in Fantasia...</font>

248
00:30:55,050 --> 00:30:57,720
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"...whose home was the Shell Mountain...</font>

249
00:30:57,890 --> 00:31:02,460
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"...somewhere in the deadly
Swamps of Sadness. "</font>

250
00:31:11,800 --> 00:31:13,970
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Come on, boy. Come on.</font>

251
00:31:27,180 --> 00:31:28,250
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">That's it.</font>

252
00:31:33,020 --> 00:31:34,190
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">It's okay.</font>

253
00:31:35,190 --> 00:31:38,820
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"Everyone knew that
whoever let the sadness overtake him...</font>

254
00:31:39,420 --> 00:31:41,490
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"...would sink into the swamp. "</font>

255
00:31:41,860 --> 00:31:43,560
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You're doing fine, Artax.</font>

256
00:31:58,970 --> 00:32:00,610
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Come on, Artax.</font>

257
00:32:06,310 --> 00:32:07,710
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What's the matter?</font>

258
00:32:08,910 --> 00:32:10,310
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What's wrong?</font>

259
00:32:16,550 --> 00:32:17,850
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Come on, boy.</font>

260
00:32:20,620 --> 00:32:22,020
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What's the matter?</font>

261
00:32:23,890 --> 00:32:25,260
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I understand.</font>

262
00:32:29,900 --> 00:32:31,700
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">It's too difficult for you.</font>

263
00:32:35,740 --> 00:32:38,540
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Artax, you're sinking! Come on!</font>

264
00:32:38,670 --> 00:32:41,470
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Turn around! You have to! Now!</font>

265
00:32:46,840 --> 00:32:49,010
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Fight against the sadness.</font>

266
00:32:51,510 --> 00:32:53,620
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Artax, please.</font>

267
00:32:53,920 --> 00:32:56,580
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Don't let the sadness
of the swamps get to you.</font>

268
00:32:57,080 --> 00:33:00,420
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You have to try. You have to care.</font>

269
00:33:01,090 --> 00:33:02,990
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">For me.</font>

270
00:33:03,060 --> 00:33:05,630
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You're my friend. I love you.</font>

271
00:33:09,960 --> 00:33:12,200
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Artax, stupid horse.</font>

272
00:33:12,900 --> 00:33:15,230
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You got to move or you'll die.</font>

273
00:33:15,600 --> 00:33:17,530
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Move. Please.</font>

274
00:33:18,440 --> 00:33:20,740
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I won't give up. Don't quit.</font>

275
00:33:20,800 --> 00:33:22,210
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Artax!</font>

276
00:34:54,710 --> 00:34:56,550
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The Shell Mountain.</font>

277
00:35:02,890 --> 00:35:05,550
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Morla, the Ancient One.</font>

278
00:35:49,760 --> 00:35:50,920
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Morla.</font>

279
00:36:56,940 --> 00:37:01,410
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But that's impossible.
They couldn't have heard me.</font>

280
00:37:02,510 --> 00:37:05,120
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Are you Morla, the Ancient One?</font>

281
00:37:10,860 --> 00:37:15,860
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Not that it matters, but yes.</font>

282
00:37:16,190 --> 00:37:19,500
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Please help me. Do you recognize this?</font>

283
00:37:20,360 --> 00:37:21,700
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Well...</font>

284
00:37:22,630 --> 00:37:24,970
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...we haven't seen...</font>

285
00:37:25,070 --> 00:37:29,040
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...the Auryn in a long time.</font>

286
00:37:29,940 --> 00:37:30,770
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">We?</font>

287
00:37:33,210 --> 00:37:34,970
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Is there someone else here, too?</font>

288
00:37:35,040 --> 00:37:39,810
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">We haven't spoken to anyone else...</font>

289
00:37:39,880 --> 00:37:43,550
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...for thousands of years.</font>

290
00:37:44,050 --> 00:37:47,750
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">So we started talking...</font>

291
00:37:47,820 --> 00:37:49,820
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...to ourselves.</font>

292
00:38:02,300 --> 00:38:04,530
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Morla, I bring terrible news.</font>

293
00:38:05,000 --> 00:38:06,930
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Did you know the Empress is ill?</font>

294
00:38:07,000 --> 00:38:10,940
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Not that it matters, but yes.</font>

295
00:38:11,570 --> 00:38:14,570
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Actually, we don't care.</font>

296
00:38:14,740 --> 00:38:16,640
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">If I don't save her, she'll die.</font>

297
00:38:16,810 --> 00:38:19,440
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">There's a terrible Nothing
sweeping over the land.</font>

298
00:38:19,510 --> 00:38:20,840
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Don't you care?</font>

299
00:38:21,080 --> 00:38:23,410
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">We don't even care...</font>

300
00:38:24,350 --> 00:38:27,420
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...whether or not we care.</font>

301
00:38:34,490 --> 00:38:35,820
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Do you have a cold?</font>

302
00:38:35,890 --> 00:38:40,230
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">No. We're allergic...</font>

303
00:38:41,130 --> 00:38:42,690
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...to youth.</font>

304
00:38:47,070 --> 00:38:49,230
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You know how to help the Empress,
don't you?</font>

305
00:38:49,300 --> 00:38:51,840
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Not that it matters...</font>

306
00:38:52,670 --> 00:38:54,840
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...but yes.</font>

307
00:38:54,900 --> 00:38:59,110
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">If you don't tell me and the Nothing
keeps coming, you'll die too. Both of you.</font>

308
00:38:59,780 --> 00:39:01,440
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Die?</font>

309
00:39:02,180 --> 00:39:05,850
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">That, at least, would be something.</font>

310
00:39:17,360 --> 00:39:19,960
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Please help me.
You said you knew the answer.</font>

311
00:39:21,030 --> 00:39:24,060
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">We're tired of sneezing.</font>

312
00:39:24,130 --> 00:39:27,900
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Go away! Nothing matters.</font>

313
00:39:28,430 --> 00:39:32,340
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">That's not true.
If it didn't matter to you, you could tell me.</font>

314
00:39:35,940 --> 00:39:37,440
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Clever boy.</font>

315
00:39:37,610 --> 00:39:38,970
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Tell me, please.</font>

316
00:39:39,670 --> 00:39:41,640
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">We don't know.</font>

317
00:39:42,840 --> 00:39:45,380
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But you can ask...</font>

318
00:39:45,680 --> 00:39:47,910
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...the Southern Oracle.</font>

319
00:39:48,050 --> 00:39:49,450
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">How can I get there?</font>

320
00:39:49,510 --> 00:39:51,150
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You can't.</font>

321
00:39:52,420 --> 00:39:57,390
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">It's 10,000 miles away.</font>

322
00:40:00,790 --> 00:40:02,760
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But that's so far.</font>

323
00:40:02,990 --> 00:40:04,630
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">That's right.</font>

324
00:40:05,490 --> 00:40:07,760
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Forget it.</font>

325
00:40:09,530 --> 00:40:11,100
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Give up.</font>

326
00:41:42,110 --> 00:41:43,270
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">No.</font>

327
00:41:45,210 --> 00:41:47,380
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Atreyu wouldn't quit now.</font>

328
00:43:23,850 --> 00:43:25,350
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Oh, boy!</font>

329
00:43:35,630 --> 00:43:38,730
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"After days and nights
of unconsciousness...</font>

330
00:43:38,960 --> 00:43:41,900
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"...Atreyu slowly opened his eyes...</font>

331
00:43:42,670 --> 00:43:46,570
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"...and found himself
in strange surroundings.</font>

332
00:43:47,340 --> 00:43:50,340
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"He was clean and
his wounds were dressed. "</font>

333
00:44:49,360 --> 00:44:51,320
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Leaving so soon?</font>

334
00:44:59,430 --> 00:45:01,400
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I was just going to....</font>

335
00:45:01,830 --> 00:45:03,530
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I have to....</font>

336
00:45:03,930 --> 00:45:05,970
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">-I was trying to--
-Sneak away?</font>

337
00:45:06,030 --> 00:45:08,500
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Yes. I mean, no.</font>

338
00:45:08,700 --> 00:45:10,370
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I like children.</font>

339
00:45:11,210 --> 00:45:12,470
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">For breakfast?</font>

340
00:45:14,140 --> 00:45:17,510
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Never. I'm a luck dragon.</font>

341
00:45:18,180 --> 00:45:20,150
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">My name is Falkor.</font>

342
00:45:21,180 --> 00:45:25,180
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">-And my name is--
-Atreyu. And you're on a quest.</font>

343
00:45:25,380 --> 00:45:26,690
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">How did you know that?</font>

344
00:45:26,780 --> 00:45:28,420
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You were unconscious.</font>

345
00:45:29,320 --> 00:45:31,050
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You talked in your sleep.</font>

346
00:45:34,060 --> 00:45:36,460
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Could you get around...</font>

347
00:45:37,360 --> 00:45:40,730
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...and scratch behind my right ear?</font>

348
00:45:41,560 --> 00:45:44,700
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I can never quite reach it.</font>

349
00:45:50,840 --> 00:45:51,740
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Here?</font>

350
00:46:02,780 --> 00:46:05,110
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">That's so good.</font>

351
00:46:06,280 --> 00:46:07,420
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Thank you.</font>

352
00:46:10,150 --> 00:46:15,020
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">So, little fellow, you're on your way
to the Southern Oracle?</font>

353
00:46:15,360 --> 00:46:17,760
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Yes. But it's hopeless.</font>

354
00:46:18,390 --> 00:46:22,430
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">-It's too far away.
-I wouldn't necessarily say that.</font>

355
00:46:23,830 --> 00:46:25,300
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You know how to get there?</font>

356
00:46:25,360 --> 00:46:28,900
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Sure. It's right around the corner.</font>

357
00:46:28,970 --> 00:46:30,800
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">How did all this happen?</font>

358
00:46:32,000 --> 00:46:33,670
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">With luck.</font>

359
00:46:34,670 --> 00:46:37,570
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You brought me the entire 10,000 miles?</font>

360
00:46:37,840 --> 00:46:43,480
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">No. Only 9,891 ...</font>

361
00:46:43,810 --> 00:46:45,750
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...as the dragon flies.</font>

362
00:46:46,450 --> 00:46:47,780
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You're amazing.</font>

363
00:46:48,120 --> 00:46:53,550
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Having a luck dragon with you
is the only way to go on a quest.</font>

364
00:46:53,920 --> 00:46:56,090
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Things will work out fine.</font>

365
00:46:57,620 --> 00:47:01,460
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Never give up and good luck will find you.</font>

366
00:47:04,130 --> 00:47:06,230
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">It's good to have a friend again.</font>

367
00:47:09,800 --> 00:47:11,970
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You have more than one.</font>

368
00:47:13,800 --> 00:47:15,140
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Look.</font>

369
00:48:12,020 --> 00:48:14,090
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Get out of my light, wench.</font>

370
00:48:14,220 --> 00:48:16,650
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You're disturbing my scientific work.</font>

371
00:48:16,720 --> 00:48:19,360
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You and your scientific work.</font>

372
00:48:19,890 --> 00:48:23,530
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What the boy needs now
is one of my potions.</font>

373
00:48:24,030 --> 00:48:28,000
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The boy will need
my scientific advice much more.</font>

374
00:48:29,560 --> 00:48:31,200
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But not until he's well.</font>

375
00:48:31,400 --> 00:48:34,700
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Get back to your own corner, Engy.</font>

376
00:48:34,940 --> 00:48:37,470
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I'm always finding you in my place.</font>

377
00:48:40,170 --> 00:48:42,010
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">He's well.</font>

378
00:48:43,140 --> 00:48:44,780
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Now it's my turn with him.</font>

379
00:48:44,840 --> 00:48:46,610
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">No, you don't!</font>

380
00:48:47,410 --> 00:48:51,080
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I'll decide when he's well.
It's your turn when I say it is.</font>

381
00:48:53,250 --> 00:48:55,590
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Well, little man, still in pain?</font>

382
00:48:56,050 --> 00:48:57,150
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">It's all right.</font>

383
00:48:57,220 --> 00:49:01,560
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I like that.
The patient telling the doctor it's all right.</font>

384
00:49:02,020 --> 00:49:04,860
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">It has to hurt if it's to heal.</font>

385
00:49:08,230 --> 00:49:09,360
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Drink that.</font>

386
00:49:11,530 --> 00:49:12,460
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Good?</font>

387
00:49:13,600 --> 00:49:15,430
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">That's my bat-wing broth.</font>

388
00:49:16,500 --> 00:49:19,700
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">There's eye of newt in there,
tree mold, old lizard brains...</font>

389
00:49:19,770 --> 00:49:23,110
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...scales from a rancid sea serpent.</font>

390
00:49:23,440 --> 00:49:27,280
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Just where did you
and your dragon come from?</font>

391
00:49:27,610 --> 00:49:29,080
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What are you on to?</font>

392
00:49:29,310 --> 00:49:32,480
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Anything of interest
to the scientific community?</font>

393
00:49:32,550 --> 00:49:35,550
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">My name is Atreyu.
I came to find the Southern Oracle.</font>

394
00:49:36,080 --> 00:49:37,420
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Here we go again.</font>

395
00:49:37,620 --> 00:49:40,390
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You've come to the right place, my boy.</font>

396
00:49:40,820 --> 00:49:43,820
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I am somewhat of an expert
on the Southern Oracle.</font>

397
00:49:43,960 --> 00:49:46,930
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"lt is my scientific specialty."</font>

398
00:49:47,260 --> 00:49:49,400
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">It is my scientific specialty.</font>

399
00:49:49,960 --> 00:49:54,700
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Why don't you sit down
and be quiet for once?</font>

400
00:49:54,800 --> 00:49:56,730
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You keep quiet, wench.</font>

401
00:49:57,130 --> 00:49:58,370
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">It's my turn.</font>

402
00:50:01,510 --> 00:50:05,740
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">My name is Engywook.
She's Urgl. Ever heard of me?</font>

403
00:50:06,070 --> 00:50:07,440
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I don't think so.</font>

404
00:50:08,080 --> 00:50:10,580
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You don't move in scientific circles.</font>

405
00:50:11,050 --> 00:50:13,810
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I am the expert on the Southern Oracle.</font>

406
00:50:14,550 --> 00:50:16,750
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You've come to the right place.</font>

407
00:50:16,820 --> 00:50:18,980
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">There's no fool like an old fool.</font>

408
00:50:19,150 --> 00:50:21,490
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Wait! Stay here.</font>

409
00:50:22,420 --> 00:50:25,590
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The observatory. To the winch, wench.</font>

410
00:50:31,030 --> 00:50:34,430
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Come on, lazybones!
Can't you go any faster?</font>

411
00:50:37,300 --> 00:50:40,640
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I've been studying
the Southern Oracle for years.</font>

412
00:50:40,840 --> 00:50:42,840
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Some day I'll publish my book:</font>

413
00:50:43,040 --> 00:50:46,710
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">A Century of Studying the Southern Oracle,
by Professor Engywook.</font>

414
00:50:47,070 --> 00:50:49,080
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Volume l.: The Early Years.</font>

415
00:50:51,210 --> 00:50:53,380
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Have you ever been
to the Southern Oracle?</font>

416
00:50:54,080 --> 00:50:55,450
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What do you think?</font>

417
00:50:55,550 --> 00:50:57,680
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I work scientifically.</font>

418
00:51:20,670 --> 00:51:21,630
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Look.</font>

419
00:51:30,380 --> 00:51:32,210
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Is that the Southern Oracle?</font>

420
00:51:32,780 --> 00:51:36,380
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">No. It's the first of the two gates
you must pass through...</font>

421
00:51:36,650 --> 00:51:39,120
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...before you reach the Southern Oracle...</font>

422
00:51:39,250 --> 00:51:42,350
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...and get me the final information
for my book.</font>

423
00:51:44,090 --> 00:51:46,920
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Of course, most people...</font>

424
00:51:47,920 --> 00:51:49,920
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...never get that far.</font>

425
00:51:51,430 --> 00:51:52,430
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Why?</font>

426
00:51:52,960 --> 00:51:54,300
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The Sphinxes' eyes...</font>

427
00:51:54,360 --> 00:51:58,960
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...stay closed until someone
who does not feel his own worth...</font>

428
00:51:59,360 --> 00:52:00,870
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...tries to pass by.</font>

429
00:52:09,940 --> 00:52:12,940
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Here comes one that looks fancy.</font>

430
00:52:18,550 --> 00:52:21,880
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Let's see what he really thinks of himself.</font>

431
00:52:29,390 --> 00:52:31,660
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Go on, scaredy-cat!</font>

432
00:52:35,260 --> 00:52:39,030
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">It's my turn. Let me see. I'm the scientist.</font>

433
00:52:39,200 --> 00:52:40,800
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">He's going on.</font>

434
00:52:42,130 --> 00:52:43,730
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I think he'll make it.</font>

435
00:52:43,900 --> 00:52:48,870
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The Sphinxes' eyes, are they open or shut?
Let me see.</font>

436
00:52:49,670 --> 00:52:51,010
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">They're shut.</font>

437
00:52:54,910 --> 00:52:56,410
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The eyes are opening!</font>

438
00:53:11,990 --> 00:53:14,430
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Did he make it? Did he?</font>

439
00:53:21,160 --> 00:53:23,500
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Fancy armor doesn't help.</font>

440
00:53:24,200 --> 00:53:28,500
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The Sphinxes can see
straight into your heart.</font>

441
00:53:32,610 --> 00:53:33,610
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Listen.</font>

442
00:53:33,810 --> 00:53:37,180
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Next time let me see what happens.
It's my telescope.</font>

443
00:53:42,010 --> 00:53:43,250
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I'm going to try.</font>

444
00:53:44,380 --> 00:53:47,650
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Don't go yet.
I haven't told you about the next gate.</font>

445
00:53:47,750 --> 00:53:49,850
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">It's even worse than this one.</font>

446
00:54:29,890 --> 00:54:33,260
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">He'll never make it.</font>

447
00:56:06,300 --> 00:56:10,030
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Don't start to doubt yourself. Be confident.</font>

448
00:56:15,540 --> 00:56:17,870
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Be confident.</font>

449
00:56:25,410 --> 00:56:26,580
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Run, Atreyu!</font>

450
00:56:27,550 --> 00:56:28,850
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Run, Atreyu!</font>

451
00:56:33,020 --> 00:56:33,980
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Run! Now!</font>

452
00:56:48,400 --> 00:56:49,700
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">He made it.</font>

453
00:56:49,930 --> 00:56:51,270
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">He made it.</font>

454
00:56:58,570 --> 00:57:01,540
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">He made it!</font>

455
00:57:05,910 --> 00:57:08,810
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You could use a dose of juicy vitamins, too.</font>

456
00:57:08,880 --> 00:57:13,720
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">He made it!
Atreyu made it through the Sphinx gate.</font>

457
00:57:14,350 --> 00:57:17,090
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">-I always said he could do it.
-Good.</font>

458
00:57:19,020 --> 00:57:22,590
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But that's no reason
to fall out of the basket again.</font>

459
00:57:23,290 --> 00:57:25,290
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I knew he'd be safe.</font>

460
00:57:25,760 --> 00:57:29,300
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Nonsense. You don't understand anything.</font>

461
00:57:30,360 --> 00:57:35,200
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The worst one is coming up.
Next is the Magic Mirror Gate.</font>

462
00:57:36,030 --> 00:57:39,040
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Atreyu must face his true self.</font>

463
00:57:39,100 --> 00:57:43,210
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">So what? That won't be too hard for him.</font>

464
00:57:43,270 --> 00:57:45,780
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">That's what everyone thinks.</font>

465
00:57:46,280 --> 00:57:49,450
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But kind people find that they are cruel.</font>

466
00:57:50,050 --> 00:57:53,820
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Brave men discover
they are really cowards.</font>

467
00:57:54,380 --> 00:57:56,850
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Confronted with their true selves...</font>

468
00:57:56,920 --> 00:58:00,420
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...most men run away screaming.</font>

469
00:59:57,080 --> 00:59:59,420
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Now, this is going too far.</font>

470
01:00:18,860 --> 01:00:20,370
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What if they...</font>

471
01:00:20,630 --> 01:00:23,970
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...really do know about me in Fantasia?</font>

472
01:01:12,840 --> 01:01:14,840
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The Southern Oracle?</font>

473
01:01:34,360 --> 01:01:36,290
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Do not be afraid.</font>

474
01:01:37,130 --> 01:01:39,300
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">We will not harm you.</font>

475
01:01:41,430 --> 01:01:45,940
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">We have been waiting for you a long time.</font>

476
01:01:50,510 --> 01:01:52,340
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Are you the Southern Oracle?</font>

477
01:01:52,810 --> 01:01:55,440
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Yes, we are.</font>

478
01:01:55,910 --> 01:01:58,580
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Then you must know
what can save Fantasia.</font>

479
01:01:59,010 --> 01:02:01,550
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Yes, we do.</font>

480
01:02:02,920 --> 01:02:05,880
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Well, what is it? I have to know!</font>

481
01:02:06,380 --> 01:02:07,690
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The Empress...</font>

482
01:02:09,120 --> 01:02:10,550
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...needs...</font>

483
01:02:11,150 --> 01:02:12,960
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...a new name.</font>

484
01:02:14,920 --> 01:02:18,530
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">A new name? That's all?</font>

485
01:02:19,160 --> 01:02:20,300
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But that's easy.</font>

486
01:02:21,860 --> 01:02:24,130
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I can give her any name she wants.</font>

487
01:02:24,570 --> 01:02:27,170
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">No one from Fantasia...</font>

488
01:02:28,170 --> 01:02:29,800
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...can do it.</font>

489
01:02:30,240 --> 01:02:32,870
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Only a human child...</font>

490
01:02:34,240 --> 01:02:36,570
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...can give her this new name.</font>

491
01:02:42,280 --> 01:02:45,110
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">A human child? Where can I find one?</font>

492
01:02:45,620 --> 01:02:47,950
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You can only find one...</font>

493
01:02:49,450 --> 01:02:53,120
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...beyond the boundaries of Fantasia.</font>

494
01:02:59,160 --> 01:03:02,000
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Ifyou want to save our world...</font>

495
01:03:02,830 --> 01:03:04,630
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...you must hurry.</font>

496
01:03:07,730 --> 01:03:09,400
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">We don't know...</font>

497
01:03:09,570 --> 01:03:13,400
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...how much longer
we can withstand the Nothing.</font>

498
01:03:17,240 --> 01:03:19,110
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Falkor!</font>

499
01:03:39,460 --> 01:03:42,130
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Hurry, Falkor! The Nothing's everywhere.</font>

500
01:03:42,230 --> 01:03:44,030
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Don't worry.</font>

501
01:03:44,860 --> 01:03:48,030
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">We'll reach the boundaries of Fantasia.</font>

502
01:03:48,130 --> 01:03:51,970
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">-Do you know where they are?
-I have no idea.</font>

503
01:03:52,900 --> 01:03:55,240
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Then how do we find a human child?</font>

504
01:03:55,570 --> 01:03:57,240
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">With luck.</font>

505
01:03:58,740 --> 01:04:01,740
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Faster, Falkor! We have to hurry.</font>

506
01:04:01,940 --> 01:04:04,780
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">All right, hang on tight.</font>

507
01:05:17,270 --> 01:05:19,910
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What a shame they don't ask me.</font>

508
01:05:20,940 --> 01:05:22,270
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">My mother...</font>

509
01:05:23,040 --> 01:05:25,710
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...she had such a wonderful name.</font>

510
01:05:41,190 --> 01:05:45,860
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"On and on they flew
until they reached the Sea of Possibilities...</font>

511
01:05:46,290 --> 01:05:48,260
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"...where they could go no further."</font>

512
01:05:50,600 --> 01:05:52,930
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Look, Atreyu. The Nothing.</font>

513
01:06:53,250 --> 01:06:54,580
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Atreyu.</font>

514
01:07:23,510 --> 01:07:25,170
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Falkor!</font>

515
01:07:29,410 --> 01:07:31,580
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Where are you?</font>

516
01:07:53,330 --> 01:07:56,500
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Atreyu! Where are you?</font>

517
01:08:48,240 --> 01:08:51,140
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">They look like big...</font>

518
01:08:51,410 --> 01:08:55,550
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...good, strong hands, don't they?</font>

519
01:08:57,210 --> 01:09:01,220
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I always thought that's what they were.</font>

520
01:09:05,750 --> 01:09:08,220
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">My little friends.</font>

521
01:09:08,660 --> 01:09:11,320
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The little man with his racing snail...</font>

522
01:09:11,630 --> 01:09:13,230
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...the Night Hob...</font>

523
01:09:13,930 --> 01:09:16,560
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...even the stupid bat.</font>

524
01:09:17,500 --> 01:09:20,330
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I couldn't hold on to them.</font>

525
01:09:21,630 --> 01:09:22,970
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The Nothing...</font>

526
01:09:24,230 --> 01:09:27,570
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...pulled them right out of my hands.</font>

527
01:09:29,140 --> 01:09:30,810
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I failed.</font>

528
01:09:31,270 --> 01:09:34,280
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">No, you didn't fail. I'm the one who failed.</font>

529
01:09:34,710 --> 01:09:37,550
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I was the one chosen to stop the Nothing.</font>

530
01:09:39,210 --> 01:09:41,050
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But I lost the Auryn.</font>

531
01:09:41,550 --> 01:09:43,720
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I can't find my luck dragon.</font>

532
01:09:44,020 --> 01:09:47,520
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">So I won't be able to get beyond
the boundaries of Fantasia.</font>

533
01:09:56,060 --> 01:09:57,390
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Listen.</font>

534
01:09:57,960 --> 01:09:59,460
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The Nothing...</font>

535
01:09:59,930 --> 01:10:01,830
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...will be here any minute.</font>

536
01:10:02,470 --> 01:10:04,970
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I will just sit here...</font>

537
01:10:05,670 --> 01:10:08,170
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...and let it take me away, too.</font>

538
01:10:09,770 --> 01:10:11,440
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">They look...</font>

539
01:10:12,310 --> 01:10:14,140
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...like good...</font>

540
01:10:14,570 --> 01:10:16,410
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...strong...</font>

541
01:10:16,610 --> 01:10:19,810
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...hands, don't they?</font>

542
01:11:22,500 --> 01:11:23,500
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Morla?</font>

543
01:11:26,930 --> 01:11:28,430
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Artax!</font>

544
01:12:19,710 --> 01:12:21,710
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">If you come any closer...</font>

545
01:12:22,910 --> 01:12:25,750
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...l will rip you to shreds.</font>

546
01:12:32,480 --> 01:12:33,950
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Who are you?</font>

547
01:12:34,050 --> 01:12:36,390
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I am Gmork.</font>

548
01:12:38,090 --> 01:12:41,260
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">And you, whoever you are...</font>

549
01:12:41,930 --> 01:12:45,660
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...can have the honor
of being my last victim.</font>

550
01:12:49,430 --> 01:12:51,130
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I will not die easily.</font>

551
01:12:51,870 --> 01:12:53,530
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I am a warrior.</font>

552
01:12:54,970 --> 01:12:56,970
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Brave warrior.</font>

553
01:12:57,510 --> 01:12:59,340
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Then fight the Nothing.</font>

554
01:12:59,410 --> 01:13:03,310
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I can't. I can't get beyond
the boundaries of Fantasia.</font>

555
01:13:05,980 --> 01:13:07,450
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What's so funny?</font>

556
01:13:07,550 --> 01:13:11,380
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Fantasia has no boundaries.</font>

557
01:13:17,720 --> 01:13:19,060
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">That's not true.</font>

558
01:13:19,390 --> 01:13:22,020
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">-You're lying.
-Foolish boy.</font>

559
01:13:23,860 --> 01:13:26,930
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Don't you know anything about Fantasia?</font>

560
01:13:27,830 --> 01:13:30,800
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">It's the world of human fantasy.</font>

561
01:13:33,330 --> 01:13:34,970
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Every part...</font>

562
01:13:35,800 --> 01:13:37,370
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...every creature...</font>

563
01:13:38,140 --> 01:13:42,470
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...is a piece of the dreams
and hopes of mankind.</font>

564
01:13:44,810 --> 01:13:46,480
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Therefore...</font>

565
01:13:47,310 --> 01:13:50,280
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...it has no boundaries.</font>

566
01:13:58,090 --> 01:14:00,060
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Why is Fantasia dying then?</font>

567
01:14:00,320 --> 01:14:04,160
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Because people have begun
to lose their hopes...</font>

568
01:14:05,430 --> 01:14:08,100
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...and forget their dreams.</font>

569
01:14:09,260 --> 01:14:12,100
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">So the Nothing grows stronger.</font>

570
01:14:12,600 --> 01:14:14,100
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What is the Nothing?</font>

571
01:14:14,370 --> 01:14:17,040
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">It's the emptiness that's left.</font>

572
01:14:18,440 --> 01:14:20,600
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">It is like a despair...</font>

573
01:14:21,110 --> 01:14:23,270
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...destroying this world.</font>

574
01:14:24,040 --> 01:14:27,140
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">And I have been trying to help it.</font>

575
01:14:29,080 --> 01:14:30,180
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But why?</font>

576
01:14:30,550 --> 01:14:33,550
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Because people who have no hopes...</font>

577
01:14:34,280 --> 01:14:36,550
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...are easy to control.</font>

578
01:14:37,950 --> 01:14:40,620
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">And whoever has the control...</font>

579
01:14:42,060 --> 01:14:44,390
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...has the power.</font>

580
01:14:59,170 --> 01:15:01,070
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Who are you, really?</font>

581
01:15:01,640 --> 01:15:03,640
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I am the servant...</font>

582
01:15:05,210 --> 01:15:08,040
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...of the power behind the Nothing.</font>

583
01:15:09,280 --> 01:15:12,610
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I was sent to kill the only one...</font>

584
01:15:13,250 --> 01:15:15,580
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...who could have stopped the Nothing.</font>

585
01:15:16,220 --> 01:15:19,550
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I lost him in the Swamps of Sadness.</font>

586
01:15:20,190 --> 01:15:21,520
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">His name...</font>

587
01:15:22,820 --> 01:15:24,160
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...was Atreyu.</font>

588
01:15:28,690 --> 01:15:32,860
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">If we're about to die anyway,
I'd rather die fighting.</font>

589
01:15:33,600 --> 01:15:37,130
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Come for me, Gmork. I am Atreyu!</font>

590
01:17:09,470 --> 01:17:10,970
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Falkor!</font>

591
01:17:20,320 --> 01:17:21,980
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Atreyu!</font>

592
01:17:44,840 --> 01:17:47,670
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"That was the end of Fantasia.</font>

593
01:17:48,400 --> 01:17:51,340
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"Only a few fragments ofthis once...</font>

594
01:17:51,570 --> 01:17:55,780
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">"...rich and beautiful world
had been left by the Nothing. "</font>

595
01:18:06,250 --> 01:18:08,090
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Good old Falkor.</font>

596
01:18:08,620 --> 01:18:12,990
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">-Can you see anything? Anything at all?
-No.</font>

597
01:18:14,290 --> 01:18:16,790
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">All the land is gone.</font>

598
01:18:17,960 --> 01:18:21,300
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I know. And all because I failed.</font>

599
01:18:22,500 --> 01:18:24,070
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You tried.</font>

600
01:18:24,500 --> 01:18:27,000
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Could the Ivory Tower still be standing?</font>

601
01:18:27,400 --> 01:18:31,640
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Let's hope so, Atreyu. Let's hope so.</font>

602
01:18:36,480 --> 01:18:38,480
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Let the Auryn guide you.</font>

603
01:18:40,210 --> 01:18:44,220
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">If the Ivory Tower still stands,
take us there.</font>

604
01:19:04,060 --> 01:19:05,700
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The Ivory Tower!</font>

605
01:20:08,980 --> 01:20:10,480
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The Empress.</font>

606
01:20:35,710 --> 01:20:37,040
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Go on.</font>

607
01:21:18,970 --> 01:21:21,810
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Why do you look so sad?</font>

608
01:21:38,690 --> 01:21:40,460
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I have failed you, Empress.</font>

609
01:21:45,190 --> 01:21:46,330
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You haven't.</font>

610
01:21:48,100 --> 01:21:49,700
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You brought him with you.</font>

611
01:21:51,770 --> 01:21:52,730
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Who?</font>

612
01:21:53,400 --> 01:21:55,600
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The earthling child.</font>

613
01:21:56,370 --> 01:21:57,940
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The one...</font>

614
01:21:58,040 --> 01:22:00,170
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...who can save us all.</font>

615
01:22:00,940 --> 01:22:03,070
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">You knew about the earthling child?</font>

616
01:22:04,180 --> 01:22:08,010
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Of course. I knew everything.</font>

617
01:22:09,580 --> 01:22:12,950
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">My horse died, I nearly drowned.</font>

618
01:22:13,220 --> 01:22:15,620
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I just barely got away from the Nothing.</font>

619
01:22:15,750 --> 01:22:18,550
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">For what? To find out
what you already knew?</font>

620
01:22:18,620 --> 01:22:21,960
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">It was the only way
to get in touch with an earthling.</font>

621
01:22:22,220 --> 01:22:24,490
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But I didn't get in touch with an earthling!</font>

622
01:22:26,260 --> 01:22:27,930
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Yes, you did.</font>

623
01:22:29,200 --> 01:22:30,630
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">He has suffered with you.</font>

624
01:22:31,860 --> 01:22:34,870
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">He went through everything
you went through.</font>

625
01:22:36,100 --> 01:22:38,940
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Andnow, he has come here...</font>

626
01:22:39,970 --> 01:22:41,040
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...with you.</font>

627
01:22:42,210 --> 01:22:45,380
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">He is very close, listening...</font>

628
01:22:46,510 --> 01:22:50,650
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...to every word we say.</font>

629
01:22:51,180 --> 01:22:52,180
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What?</font>

630
01:23:07,330 --> 01:23:11,060
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Where is he?
lf he's so close, why doesn't he arrive?</font>

631
01:23:16,400 --> 01:23:21,240
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">He doesn't realize
he's already part of The Neverending Story.</font>

632
01:23:23,710 --> 01:23:25,510
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">The Neverending Story?</font>

633
01:23:25,570 --> 01:23:27,180
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What's that?</font>

634
01:23:27,240 --> 01:23:30,710
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Just as he is sharing all your adventures...</font>

635
01:23:30,810 --> 01:23:33,310
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...others are sharing his.</font>

636
01:23:33,850 --> 01:23:35,110
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">They were with him...</font>

637
01:23:35,480 --> 01:23:38,320
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...when he hid from the boys
in the bookstore.</font>

638
01:23:40,920 --> 01:23:42,620
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But that's impossible!</font>

639
01:23:42,850 --> 01:23:45,360
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">They were with him
when he took the book...</font>

640
01:23:45,520 --> 01:23:47,590
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...with the Auryn symbol on the cover...</font>

641
01:23:48,730 --> 01:23:52,030
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...in which he's reading his own story...</font>

642
01:23:52,900 --> 01:23:54,400
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...right now.</font>

643
01:23:59,900 --> 01:24:01,900
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I can't believe it.</font>

644
01:24:03,370 --> 01:24:05,710
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">They can't be talking about me.</font>

645
01:24:08,980 --> 01:24:11,010
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What if he doesn't appear?</font>

646
01:24:11,080 --> 01:24:13,480
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Then our world will disappear.</font>

647
01:24:14,480 --> 01:24:16,150
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">And so will l.</font>

648
01:24:19,480 --> 01:24:21,250
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">How could he let that happen?</font>

649
01:24:21,350 --> 01:24:26,120
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">He doesn't understand that he's the one
with the power to stop it.</font>

650
01:24:26,220 --> 01:24:28,660
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">He simply can't imagine...</font>

651
01:24:28,720 --> 01:24:31,590
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...that one little boy
could be that important.</font>

652
01:24:34,400 --> 01:24:35,860
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Is it really me?</font>

653
01:24:36,830 --> 01:24:38,430
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Maybe he doesn't know what to do.</font>

654
01:24:38,900 --> 01:24:40,370
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What do I have to do?</font>

655
01:24:41,140 --> 01:24:44,100
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">He has to give me a new name.</font>

656
01:24:44,470 --> 01:24:46,610
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">He's already chosen it.</font>

657
01:24:47,740 --> 01:24:49,710
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">He just has to call it out.</font>

658
01:24:53,580 --> 01:24:56,080
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But it's only a story. It's not real.</font>

659
01:24:56,210 --> 01:24:57,280
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">It's only a story.</font>

660
01:24:58,820 --> 01:25:00,780
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Atreyu, no!</font>

661
01:25:25,500 --> 01:25:27,170
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Bastian!</font>

662
01:25:29,240 --> 01:25:32,910
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Why don't you do
what you dream, Bastian?</font>

663
01:25:33,240 --> 01:25:36,680
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">But I can't.
I must keep my feet on the ground.</font>

664
01:25:36,980 --> 01:25:38,650
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Call my name.</font>

665
01:25:41,250 --> 01:25:44,250
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Bastian, please!</font>

666
01:25:46,250 --> 01:25:47,590
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Save us!</font>

667
01:25:47,650 --> 01:25:49,760
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">All right! I'll do it!</font>

668
01:25:50,020 --> 01:25:53,730
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I'll save you. I will do what I dream.</font>

669
01:26:18,910 --> 01:26:20,920
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Why is it so dark?</font>

670
01:26:21,780 --> 01:26:25,620
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">In the beginning, it is always dark.</font>

671
01:26:30,620 --> 01:26:32,120
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What is that?</font>

672
01:26:32,690 --> 01:26:34,860
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">One grain of sand.</font>

673
01:26:35,490 --> 01:26:39,160
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">It is all that remains of my vast empire.</font>

674
01:26:47,000 --> 01:26:49,770
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Fantasia has totally disappeared?</font>

675
01:26:51,270 --> 01:26:52,770
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Yes.</font>

676
01:26:55,640 --> 01:26:58,140
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Then everything's been in vain.</font>

677
01:26:58,980 --> 01:27:01,150
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">No, it hasn't.</font>

678
01:27:02,480 --> 01:27:05,120
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Fantasia can arise anew...</font>

679
01:27:06,720 --> 01:27:09,350
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...from your dreams and wishes.</font>

680
01:27:11,190 --> 01:27:12,320
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">How?</font>

681
01:27:13,120 --> 01:27:14,930
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Open your hand.</font>

682
01:27:29,870 --> 01:27:32,010
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What are you going to wish for?</font>

683
01:27:34,270 --> 01:27:35,570
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">I don't know.</font>

684
01:27:37,410 --> 01:27:41,250
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Then there will be no Fantasia anymore.</font>

685
01:27:45,750 --> 01:27:47,480
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">How many wishes do I get?</font>

686
01:27:49,090 --> 01:27:51,050
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">As many as you want.</font>

687
01:27:51,920 --> 01:27:54,390
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">And the more wishes you make...</font>

688
01:27:54,920 --> 01:27:58,560
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...the more magnificent
Fantasia will become.</font>

689
01:27:58,860 --> 01:28:00,030
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Really?</font>

690
01:28:00,960 --> 01:28:02,430
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Try it.</font>

691
01:28:15,670 --> 01:28:17,470
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Then my first wish is....</font>

692
01:28:26,720 --> 01:28:29,650
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Falkor, it's even more beautiful
than I thought!</font>

693
01:28:40,690 --> 01:28:44,200
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">-Like it?
-Falkor, it's wonderful.</font>

694
01:28:49,170 --> 01:28:52,840
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Falkor, it's like the Nothing never was.</font>

695
01:29:11,650 --> 01:29:13,820
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Atreyu and Artax!</font>

696
01:29:27,430 --> 01:29:30,430
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">What would you like to wish for next?</font>

697
01:30:00,360 --> 01:30:02,320
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Look, there they are.</font>

698
01:30:03,860 --> 01:30:05,330
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">It's a monster!</font>

699
01:30:06,500 --> 01:30:10,300
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Get them, Falkor!
Let's see how you like it, chickens.</font>

700
01:30:10,630 --> 01:30:11,970
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Down here.</font>

701
01:30:26,580 --> 01:30:29,010
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">We're going to get you!</font>

702
01:30:54,900 --> 01:30:57,070
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">Bastian made many other wishes...</font>

703
01:30:57,700 --> 01:31:00,370
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...and had many other
amazing adventures...</font>

704
01:31:01,470 --> 01:31:04,470
<font face="Cronos Pro Light" size="38" color="#fcffda">...before he finally returned
to the ordinary world.</font>

